"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:32:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解grad一定要去trip？</blockquote><br />\n人有我有既心態<br />\n覺得唔去=冇面<br />\n窮撚都要借錢去</blockquote><br />\n點解一定要去? +1<br />\n最後一個暑假 可以做啲有意義既野充實自己<br />\n點解一定要跟人地條路行<br />\n自己既人生自己決定</blockquote><br />\n有咩可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇grad trip去日日喺屋企做緊廢青</blockquote><br />\n每人對'有意義'既definition都唔同<br />\n本身自己有興趣既趁依家做下 之後返工唔會有呢啲機會</blockquote><br />\n去睇下人地國家嘅環境係點(去完發覺香港交通個啲係幾正幾方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n趁班fd都係grad ，大家有時間又有力，心境又差唔多，咪大家去玩下啲<br />\n唔一定有咩特别目的，咪當係學生生涯嘅完結"},{"pid":"010a731ff4ffd4a51c44bc86edc0824d2ee27178","tid":304743,"uid":104684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T13:07:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>因為冇朋友</blockquote><br />\n自己去<br />\n我都打算自己去</blockquote><br />\n自己去會唔會好難...<br />\n巴打念住去邊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為我都預見到我都係無朋友所以要自己去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n台北<br />\n唔知難唔難，未試過。我去過一次旅行only (跟團)。<br />\n我諗有手機 網絡 錢 就生存到。"},{"pid":"bcc43703f4e81e7dac88230c6ea71a69a1bf2a38","tid":304743,"uid":91259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T13:11:26.000Z","msg":"Hd 果陣已經借錢讀書 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n讀part time 又要反工又要比家用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n那有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0daf50088bfd5b6309ed95e8cd103282cf86c41","tid":304743,"uid":6688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T13:12:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8500ff7bdc383f2b2be51e721cc86a03a616b780","tid":304743,"uid":89166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"re