咁開心"},{"pid":"b7b78dd5d8b3202d494211f5d6492f80f3cef491","tid":304743,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T00:52:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解grad一定要去trip？</blockquote><br />\n有朋友同我講：你宜家未洗返工，可以盡情玩，之後返左工去旅行就要就住就住。Grad trip 是你人生最後的自由之旅。</blockquote><br />\n最難係約人<br />\n響香港食餐飯都難<br />\n仲去咩旅行<br />\n同埋有時間去旅行都留比另一半啦"},{"pid":"95a984e379fe15d5081435c6a4f775578402d355","tid":304743,"uid":11696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T01:11:25.000Z","msg":"我認為值得去，<br />\n首先，你唔會再有機會一班人一齊去，返工之後，你想食餐飯都極困難，亦有唔少人會從此消失，FB/IG都可能未必見到佢...<br />\n假期，返工之後你想要10日以上假期極度困難，<br />\n除非轉工，<br />\n但係人大左好多負擔，全屋 屋租差响水電煤全部靠我俾，邊度有咁多餘錢去旅行？<br />\n心態，而家比較，學生時代絕對係自由自在，<br />\n你返工之後，24hr on call,就算係外地，老闆係時刻招換你既。<br />\n平平地幾千蚊去幾日東南亞國家/ 去歐洲美洲就要一早計劃儲錢唔係話去就去，<br />\n個人認為返吓Parttime唔困難，做吓茶餐廳M記之類都儲到，而且可以見識吓呢個社會"},{"pid":"2bbf8a766931c34fa68aa4559ccd95ae1e96b081","tid":304743,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T01:15:47.000Z","msg":"借左朋友一萬蚊去六星期摩洛哥+一個月其他歐洲地方<br />\n<br />\n反正畢業之後都會返工，出糧再還"},{"pid":"1680cfa65eaf36810c35f65ce336d1dc751f9d1b","tid":304743,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T01:25:12.000Z","msg":"yr3已經預先去左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後冇去了<br />\n讀cs冇時間返partime<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9fbf3a12ab0860251051617ff43890666b3c900","tid":304743,"uid":54488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T03:22:19.000Z","msg":"純粹唔鍾意去旅行"},{"pid":"d579d5666291f29cb116dcf4310afaca782d9235","tid":304743,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T03:36:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>FYP 用撚左咁多錢<br />\n<br />\n仲點去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做咩FYP 要自己俾錢... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好明顯係請槍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nDesign科fyp燒錢到你唔信<br />\n服裝要買大量配件大量布要請model<br />\n電影類fyp要租場租器材請演員<br />\n全部都係錢<br />\n請槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nI know that feel bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌佢筆直完全唔夠做個project 要自己貼錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d954bcef957df63e64bcd44f68f9199b68651bf","tid":304743,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T04:24:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為冇朋友</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c241aabba4ab9d3b24c11c9ceb02907272866c65","tid":304743,"uid":81028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:52:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因為冇朋友</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n咁你有無錢?"},{"pid":"6f4ac9b070df8a49c85d9bbfe8490142ff0362a2","tid":304743,"uid":91220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:57:37.000Z","msg":"冇朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7f0a6c4db1ffe3fa664b5556df53b45efeba6bf","tid":304743,"uid":6688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T14:56:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}